name: test_authorization_with_invalid_login
description:
Steps
        1. Open main page
        2. Click on the link "Вход"
        3. Find field "Логин"
        4. Fill field "Логин" with invalid data
        5. Find field "Пароль"
        6. Fill field "Пароль" with valid data
        7. Click on the button "Вход"
        8. Check authorization.
